data.description: Check out this 4 bed 2 bath ranch home in Caro! Set on 28 acres, with 25ish acres of woods, this property offers plenty of space for peace, privacy & hunting. Conveniently located off M-46, with road access on Bruisee and Leix Rd. Kitchen has been updated and has a newer roof. Garage is extra deep at 27' and has a 16x24 pole barn. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own your own property—schedule a showing today!
